there is no tomorrow.

00:16.554 --> 00:18.251
If your story is true--

00:18.425 --> 00:21.124
a government agency waging
an illegal war,

00:21.298 --> 00:22.908
dealing drugs--

00:23.082 --> 00:24.562
well, then you of all people
should know that there's nothing

00:24.736 --> 00:26.694
they won't do
to kill that story.

00:26.868 --> 00:28.044
Need to be begging
for forgiveness,

00:28.218 --> 00:29.523
all the shit
you done put us through.

00:29.697 --> 00:30.872
