in front of the bullet,

00:31.047 --> 00:32.439
like I always have,

00:32.613 --> 00:33.919
to keep y'all safe.

00:34.093 --> 00:36.487
Now let me get us out of this,

00:36.661 --> 00:39.185
like I got us out of every
other motherfucking thing else!

00:39.359 --> 00:40.752
MANBOY:
When I tell you
that I'm-a kill Leon

00:40.926 --> 00:42.275
and Franklin for what
they did to your baby,

00:42.449 --> 00:44.103
I mean that.

00:44.277 --> 00:46.366
How's your brother doing?

00:46.540 --> 00:48.716
Uh, what made you think of him?

00:48.890 --> 00:52.590
I just know he was transferred
from CYA to Chino, right?

00:52.764 --> 00:54.983
Wonder how he's getting along.

00:55.158 --> 00:56.855
-You saw who it was, right?
-[gunshots]

00:57.029 --> 00:58.161
[Louie screams]

00:58.335 --> 01:00.250
It was that little girl's mama.

01:00.424 --> 01:01.816
JEROME:
The minute I finish
sitting with her,

01:01.990 --> 01:03.688
we're gonna get
these motherfuckers.

01:03.862 --> 01:05.124
TANOSSE:
They got Louie.

01:05.298 --> 01:06.212
And just so you know,

01:06.386 --> 01:07.387
Jerome and his folks

01:07.561 --> 01:08.562
talking a lot of shit.

01:08.736 --> 01:10.434
Gonna come at you tonight.

01:10.608 --> 01:11.783
Let 'em come.

01:11.957 --> 01:13.611
