01:27.277 --> 01:28.626
TANOSSE:
Me and my girls

01:28.800 --> 01:30.845
was out at the Red Onion
for my birthday.

01:31.019 --> 01:32.804
Was having a good time,

01:32.978 --> 01:34.545
