at first, but...

01:36.808 --> 01:39.202
FRANKLIN:
But he remembered you.

01:39.376 --> 01:42.030
That you and me had our thing
back in the day.

01:42.205 --> 01:43.945
Said y'all was cool now.

01:44.120 --> 01:45.599
Partners.

01:46.818 --> 01:49.516
Few weeks later,
he shows up at the shop.

01:49.690 --> 01:52.563
Figured he was trying
to get some, you know.

01:52.737 --> 01:55.261
