02:10.276 --> 02:11.886
like I never meant shit to you.

02:12.060 --> 02:13.801
That was a long time ago.

02:13.975 --> 02:16.064
But since you went there,

02:16.239 --> 02:18.415
I remember
I was real important to you

02:18.589 --> 02:20.243
