10:17.720 --> 10:18.764
Said you'd know it.

10:18.938 --> 10:20.679
I know the place.

10:20.853 --> 10:23.247
Tell him
me and mine'll be there.

10:39.959 --> 10:41.569
You okay?

10:41.744 --> 10:43.441
Mm-hmm.

10:45.704 --> 10:48.359
You sure about this?

10:58.325 --> 11:00.763
