I realized I had two options.

24:18.298 --> 24:20.213
I could either
sit there and feel stupid,

24:20.387 --> 24:24.435
or I could go get some
motherfucking revenge.

24:24.609 --> 24:26.481
See what page I'm on?

24:26.655 --> 24:30.267
