so when all this shit play out,

24:30.441 --> 24:32.791
I'm-a need a piece
of that bounty.

24:37.274 --> 24:39.537
You know where he at right now?

24:39.711 --> 24:42.758
AVI:
Mushrooms are by far

24:42.932 --> 24:45.848
my favorite psychedelic.

24:46.022 --> 24:47.850
All natural.

24:48.024 --> 24:50.548
