for a little while longer?

25:27.716 --> 25:31.241
You learn nothing, huh?

25:31.415 --> 25:35.158
Trying to clean this up
will only hurt you.

25:35.332 --> 25:38.074
The job will never be finished.

25:38.248 --> 25:40.032
There'll always be another war,

25:40.206 --> 25:41.860
another loose end to snip.

25:43.253 --> 25:46.909
If you really
want to stay involved...

25:47.083 --> 25:49.215
there are other ways.

25:50.260 --> 25:52.567
You're smart, you're connected,

25:52.741 --> 25:54.307
you know my business.

25:54.481 --> 25:57.702
And it seems to me, as of now,
you're unemployed.

26:00.575 --> 26:02.925
Look.

26:03.099 --> 26:05.101
You gave everything
to your country.

26:05.275 --> 26:06.450
I know how it is.

26:06.624 --> 26:09.540
You bought into the dream.

26:10.759 --> 26:14.676
It's time to cash in
on the reality.

26:19.463 --> 26:21.465
Appreciate the offer, man.

26:23.032 --> 26:24.686
I'll let you know.

26:26.122 --> 26:27.558
BLACK DIAMOND:
This where Leon at?

26:27.732 --> 26:29.386
WANDA:
Yep.

26:29.560 --> 26:31.649
This the spot.

26:31.823 --> 26:35.653
He and that ho
in that room right there.

26:35.827 --> 26:37.829
Just got to wait on him
to come out.

26:38.003 --> 26:40.440
How you know what room they in?

26:40.615 --> 26:42.312
'Cause I followed them.

26:42.486 --> 26:44.314
How you follow them
if you ain't got no car?

26:44.488 --> 26:46.969
My homegirl drove me.

26:47.143 --> 26:48.100
[tires screeching]

26:48.274 --> 26:49.754
Sh...

26:51.843 --> 26:53.410
Told you we should've never
trusted Wanda's ass.

26:53.584 --> 26:56.456
-Get your ass out...
-WANDA: No... [stammers]

27:00.765 --> 27:02.114
DALLAS:
Take another step and I'm-a blow

27:02.288 --> 27:03.681
-this bitch head off.
-Lee.

27:03.855 --> 27:05.465
You ain't say nothing
about no gun to my head.

27:05.640 --> 27:07.293
FRANKLIN:
All right.

27:07.467 --> 27:09.905
Y'all ain't got to hurt Wanda.
We just want to talk.

27:10.079 --> 27:11.994
-Yeah, right.
-You must be out your damn mind.

27:12.168 --> 27:13.822
FRANKLIN:
This ain't what it look like.

27:13.996 --> 27:16.999
Ain't no hard feelings.

27:17.173 --> 27:19.741
We know it wasn't personal
with Louie.

27:19.915 --> 27:21.699
Y'all was just chasing money.

27:21.873 --> 27:26.748
Right? Well, the good news is
we got more money than God.

27:26.922 --> 27:28.445
So why not work with us?

27:28.619 --> 27:29.968
We don't work for niggas.

27:30.142 --> 27:31.404
Then work withus.

27:31.578 --> 27:32.667
DALLAS:
Until you get what you want

27:32.841 --> 27:34.712
and Jerome
fucking kills us, right?

27:34.886 --> 27:37.019
You can't tell me
he ain't still mad about Louie.

27:37.193 --> 27:38.498
Oh, he's mad.

27:38.673 --> 27:41.371
But he understands the game.

27:41.545 --> 27:46.376
What we're offering y'all
is a home.

27:46.550 --> 27:48.421
Y'all got to be tired
of being free agents.

27:48.595 --> 27:49.640
Out here in the jungle.

27:49.814 --> 27:52.861
Only able to eat what you kill.

27:53.035 --> 27:56.038
You fuck with us,
you'll be on call.

27:56.212 --> 27:58.475
But you ain't got
to scramble for every meal.

28:01.043 --> 28:04.655
I'm offering y'all
full-time employment.

28:04.829 --> 28:06.570
Stability.

28:06.744 --> 28:09.051
Hold up. How you gonna offer
these bitches a job before me?

28:09.225 --> 28:10.705
Wanda, you already
working with us.

28:10.879 --> 28:12.358
What the fuck
you think you doing right now?

28:12.532 --> 28:14.447
JEROME:
Hey!

28:14.621 --> 28:17.276
Y'all got one chance
to come out the cold.

28:17.450 --> 28:19.888
You turn this down,
you gonna be on the other side,

28:20.062 --> 28:22.020
and y'all asses
ain't gonna want that.

28:25.415 --> 28:27.809
Plenty more
where that came from.

28:33.553 --> 28:36.034
Fuck it.

28:36.208 --> 28:37.732
