28:46.218 --> 28:48.220
-Yeah.
-Damn, babe, why you ain't get

28:48.394 --> 28:50.092
-the name-brand Q-tips?
-Yeah, all right.

28:50.266 --> 28:52.050
These ain't about shit.

29:03.496 --> 29:05.542
Black Diamond and Dallas,
they got Leon.

29:09.024 --> 29:11.417
What's up?
You coming?

29:16.727 --> 29:19.382
If you can't get with this,

29:19.556 --> 29:22.777
then we ain't got
shit else to discuss.

29:25.605 --> 29:27.433
-Khadijah.
-[door opens]

29:27.607 --> 29:29.958
-Khadijah!
-[door closes]

29:30.132 --> 29:31.568
-[billiard balls clack]
-♪ ♪

29:33.831 --> 29:35.572
[sighs]

29:40.533 --> 29:42.318
TEDDY:
I don't suppose
that's all about me, is it?

29:42.492 --> 29:45.060
Motherfucker.

29:47.279 --> 29:48.890
Can I sit?

29:58.813 --> 30:01.163
[sighs]

30:01.337 --> 30:04.906
Wow, you know, after
that radio interview of yours,

30:05.080 --> 30:07.386
my boss was...

30:07.560 --> 30:09.693
not exactly thrilled.

30:09.867 --> 30:12.000
That was the idea, asshole.

30:12.174 --> 30:14.176
[laughs softly]

30:16.221 --> 30:18.658
I want you to know
that I'm sorry

30:18.833 --> 30:21.313
for what happened.

30:21.487 --> 30:22.749
What I did.

30:22.924 --> 30:24.534
I just thought
that it's what I had to.

30:24.708 --> 30:26.144
I thought I was doing
the right thing.

30:26.318 --> 30:28.538
No. Stop.
What... what is this?

30:28.712 --> 30:32.107
What-what are you doing?

30:32.281 --> 30:34.457
You want to scare me some more?
Because it won't work.

30:34.631 --> 30:37.329
They're cutting me out.

30:37.503 --> 30:39.505
I'm done.

30:42.378 --> 30:44.075
See, things got a little messy,

30:44.249 --> 30:46.469
so they're gonna
toss me off the ship

30:46.643 --> 30:49.472
I built from scratch
with my bare fucking hands.

30:51.126 --> 30:52.910
And whatever it is
you think of me,

30:53.084 --> 30:55.391
I have sacrificed everything

30:55.565 --> 30:57.697
for this mission.

30:57.872 --> 31:00.135
For their mission.

31:00.309 --> 31:02.659
I feel no pity for you.

31:04.269 --> 31:07.664
You get no absolution from me,
if that's what you want.

31:08.665 --> 31:09.971
I'm not looking for anything,

31:10.145 --> 31:11.886
I just wanted
to give you something.

31:15.498 --> 31:16.716
You have your tape recorder?

31:20.285 --> 31:22.331
