need a drink first.

31:51.142 --> 31:54.232
-You want another one?
-Whiskey. Neat.

32:00.369 --> 32:02.371
TEDDY:
Uh, two Jamesons, please. Neat.

32:02.545 --> 32:03.981
BARTENDER:
You got it.

32:04.155 --> 32:06.157
-[billiard balls clack]
-[laughter]

32:06.331 --> 32:08.725
[indistinct chatter]

32:19.344 --> 32:21.259
-BARTENDER: There you go.
-[cash register dings]

32:46.154 --> 32:48.460
Okay.

32:48.634 --> 32:50.158
I'm ready when you are.

32:58.993 --> 33:02.213
My name is Teddy McDonald,

33:02.387 --> 33:04.999
and I'm an officer with the
Central Intelligence Agency.

33:05.173 --> 33:10.091
In summer of '83, I was
approached by Alejandro Usteves.

33:10.265 --> 33:12.615
He's a Nicaraguan national.
He's also a CIA asset.

33:12.789 --> 33:15.444
-[door shuts loudly]
-[dog barking nearby]

33:23.147 --> 33:25.497
