-[scoffs]

33:27.673 --> 33:29.936
KHADIJAH:
Look, whatever the fuck
they giving you,

33:30.111 --> 33:32.678
I'll triple it.

33:32.852 --> 33:34.680
[chuckles]

33:36.204 --> 33:39.511
FRANKLIN:
Triple ain't even gonna
come close.

33:46.475 --> 33:49.695
