33:59.879 --> 34:02.534
I just want to apologize.

34:05.581 --> 34:09.019
If I could change shit,
I would.

34:09.193 --> 34:11.543
Yeah, but you can't.

34:13.937 --> 34:15.982
And now I'm gonna haunt you

34:16.157 --> 34:18.202
