You didn't even have to do that.

34:48.145 --> 34:50.539
[Khadijah breathing erratically]

34:55.979 --> 34:58.938
FRANKLIN:
Leon...

34:59.113 --> 35:01.419
let's go.

35:05.815 --> 35:07.164
Leon.

35:07.338 --> 35:09.993
Come on.

35:10.167 --> 35:11.299
Let her go, man.

35:11.473 --> 35:14.606
Come on.
Come on.

35:38.413 --> 35:40.023
TEDDY:
Sorry.

35:40.197 --> 35:42.982
[siren wailing in distance]

35:43.157 --> 35:44.375
Don't touch me.

35:44.549 --> 35:45.985
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

35:46.160 --> 35:47.465
I'm just...

35:47.639 --> 35:49.554
just trying
to make sure you're okay.

35:49.728 --> 35:52.427
I'm fine.
It's these fucking shoes.

35:52.601 --> 35:53.732
Why don't we just
call you a cab.

35:53.906 --> 35:56.039
I said I'm fine.

35:56.213 --> 35:59.129
This... this doesn't make you
a good person, you know?

36:01.044 --> 36:02.828
