for what you've done.

36:03.002 --> 36:04.830
I know.

36:05.004 --> 36:07.485
I just don't really know
what else to do at this point.

36:11.185 --> 36:13.404
So if you need anything more,

36:13.578 --> 36:16.451
you know where to find me.

36:16.625 --> 36:18.496
Good night.

36:23.806 --> 36:25.808
[car door shuts]

36:29.028 --> 36:31.857
[engine starts]

36:48.613 --> 36:50.485
[monitor beeping steadily]

37:13.943 --> 37:16.424
How long before you leave?

37:16.598 --> 37:18.208
I ain't going nowhere.

37:22.821 --> 37:24.954
What about Top Notch
and the passports?

37:25.128 --> 37:27.217
No, that was for us,
but if you're not with me,

37:27.391 --> 37:29.437
then I ain't going.

37:35.791 --> 37:37.314
Just came to check on you.

37:37.488 --> 37:41.057
See if there was
anything I could do.

37:46.410 --> 37:51.241
I am so tired, Alton.

37:55.289 --> 37:57.421
[sighs]

38:10.260 --> 38:12.784
FRANKLIN:
What are you doing?

38:24.622 --> 38:26.450
What happened to you?

38:26.624 --> 38:28.626
What the fuck
are you doing here?

38:32.326 --> 38:34.023
I came to check on your mother.

38:34.197 --> 38:37.026
Nigga, that ain't
your job no more.

39:48.880 --> 39:50.665
[horn blaring]

39:59.630 --> 40:01.415
[horn stops]

40:09.945 --> 40:13.209
[muffled shout]

40:45.154 --> 40:46.982
REPORTER:
The driver has been identified

40:47.156 --> 40:49.506
as local news reporter
Irene Abe,

40:49.680 --> 40:52.596
formerly of
theHerald Examiner.

40:52.770 --> 40:54.337
MALE REPORTER:
Thank you, Julie.
This story is developing,

40:54.511 --> 40:57.383
so we'll follow it
if we hear anything further.

40:57.558 --> 41:00.038
The financial crisis for
American farmers continues...

41:00.212 --> 41:02.040
[reporter continues
indistinctly]

41:02.214 --> 41:04.478
-[indistinct chatter]
-[phone rings]

41:12.007 --> 41:13.791
I'll be right back.

41:24.062 --> 41:25.977
How you doing?

41:26.151 --> 41:29.154
FRANKLIN:
Good. Saw on the news
what happened with Irene.

41:32.549 --> 41:33.855
Yeah, no, don't drink and drive.

41:34.029 --> 41:36.379
