do about your father.

41:54.136 --> 41:56.834
REPORTER:
LAPD sources have confirmed
that Ms. Abe was

41:57.008 --> 41:58.706
indeed under the influence,

41:58.880 --> 42:01.970
and it is being classified as a fatal drunk driving accident.

42:02.144 --> 42:04.625
Mothers Against Drunk Driving
spoke out strongly,

42:04.799 --> 42:07.062
[echoing]: expressing sympathy
for her family

42:07.236 --> 42:08.629
and pointing out...

42:08.803 --> 42:11.501
[reporter continues
indistinctly]

42:11.675 --> 42:13.677
